    <title type="html"><![CDATA[How to Remove Programs From the Start Up in Mac OS X]]></title>
    <link href="http://amejiarosario.github.io/blog/2011/11/18/how-to-remove-programs-from-the-start-up-in-mac-os-x/"/>
